(Plantaobot - One-Page App Summary) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What it is) Tj
T*
(- Plantaobot is a React + Vite demo interface for an AI-assisted medical shift capture workflow.) Tj
T*
(- It simulates triage of shift offers, manual swipe decisions, and performance tracking in a single UI.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Who it is for) Tj
T*
(- Primary persona: physicians in Brazil who monitor medical shift groups and want faster, criteria-based shift selection.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What it does) Tj
T*
(- Onboards the user and stores profile/preferences locally.) Tj
T*
(- Simulates incoming group feed messages with offers and non-offer noise.) Tj
T*
(- Scores shift offers by value, distance, day, and specialty preferences.) Tj
T*
(- Auto-captures qualified offers \(or routes them to manual swipe review\).) Tj
T*
(- Tracks captured/rejected/pending offers with dashboard and insights views.) Tj
T*
(- Exports captured shifts to CSV.) Tj
T*
(- Provides notifications, onboarding/settings controls, and a contextual AI chat panel.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(How it works \(repo-evidenced architecture\)) Tj
T*
(- Frontend: Single-page React app bootstrapped by Vite; App.jsx orchestrates tabs/state.) Tj
T*
(- Data layer: Static mock datasets \(SHIFTS/NOISE/MONTHLY/GROUPS\) drive simulation.) Tj
T*
(- Decision engine: calcScore\(\) in utils computes a 0-100 score from user preferences.) Tj
T*
(- Persistence: useLocalStorage hook stores name, screen, captured shifts, groups, and prefs in browser localStorage.) Tj
T*
(- UI modules: tab components \(Dashboard/Feed/Swipe/Captured/Insights/Settings\) plus AIChat, modals, notifications, and shared UI widgets.) Tj
T*
(- Data flow: startBot\(\) schedules timed feed events -> scoring -> captured/rejected/pending arrays -> dashboard/insights totals and CSV export.) Tj
T*
(- Backend/API: Not found in repo.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(How to run \(minimal\)) Tj
T*
(- Requirements: Node.js 18+ and npm 9+.) Tj
T*
(- Install: npm install) Tj
T*
(- Start dev server: npm run dev) Tj
ET
